                     <interp inst="t18270913-220-person1928" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I am an officer. I apprehended the prisoner. I received the bundle.(Property produced and sworn to.)</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I never saw the bundle.</p>
